 (172.16.6.91)
X-YovoleRuleAgent: yovoleflag

PolarFire implements specific PCIe interrupts besides PLDA
local interrupt. For PLDA lack of MSI controller, these
interrupts can not be added to MSI. Polar driver also register
these interrupt symbol name.

PolarFire PCIe contain total 28 interrupts event while PLDA
contain 13 local interrupts event, interrupt to event
num mapping is different.

So add a callback function to support different IRQ register
function. Also Add PLDA default handler function, which will
be moved to pcie-plda-host.c in moving codes patch.

Signed-off-by: Minda Chen <minda.chen@starfivetech.com>
Acked-by: Conor Dooley <conor.dooley@microchip.com>
